434
00:31:49,729 --> 00:31:51,623
<i>Sirkus P.T. Barnum.</i>

435
00:31:55,971 --> 00:31:57,055
Lewat sini.

436
00:31:57,179 --> 00:32:00,247
Bukankah sudah cukup 'percaya buta'
