438
00:32:04,270 --> 00:32:05,687
Kau siap?

439
00:32:12,277 --> 00:32:14,450
Itu rumah kita?/
Benar.

440
00:32:16,866 --> 00:32:18,907
Mari kita pergi.

441
00:32:19,284 --> 00:32:20,577
Dorong.

442
00:32:25,707 --> 00:32:27,460
Helen, itu untukmu.

443
00:32:30,251 --> 00:32:33,754
