Ada sekolah balet tepat
di ujung jalan.

445
00:32:43,506 --> 00:32:45,078
Melewati rumah orang tuamu.

446
00:32:47,479 --> 00:32:49,268
Jangan bilang kau beli rumah ini...

447
00:32:49,468 --> 00:32:51,768
